
The following chat lines exist for wizard staff only. Mortals do not
receive any of these lines. Player communication uses in-game radios,
telepathy (after introduction), say/whisper in a room, and tell to staff.

Wizard staff lines:

newbie          fighter
kataan          cleric
mage            monk
rogue           hm
cre             admin (arch wizards only)
gossip          council (council members)

The command to use each line is the name of the line. You may also send
emotes over the chat lines by appending "emote" onto the command name.
Example:

newbieemote smiles at everyone.

Would show to people:

<newbie> Descartes smiles at everyone.

To see who all is online on a line, use the command "list". Example:
"list newbie".

Players (mortals) should use:
  radio <message>     in-game radio on your frequency
  telepathy <who> <msg>   psionic contact (requires introduction)
  tell <staff> <msg>      contact online wizard staff
  ooc <message>       global out-of-character channel

See also: communication, radio, telepathy, introduce, wiz, ooc
